snippet.title: New Bodycam footage of police is proof that amber lied about a "messy crime scene"
snippet.description:
In uk court, Amber heard said under oath that it was a big crime scene and that the floor was stained with wine, glasses were shattered everything was messy. But here in this new evidence from team depp is opposite from everything she said. video via @Daily Mail
